Drowsebook website & promotional assets
========================================

The contents of this repository — the landing page (`index.html`,
`privacy.html`, `terms.html`, `styles.css`, `i18n.js`, `404.html`,
`README.md` and its translations), and the icons and posters under
`icons/` and `posters/` — are © 2026 hooosberg. All rights reserved.

The iOS app **Drowsebook (入梦书)** itself is closed-source. The source
code is not contained in this repository.

If you would like to reuse any text or images here — for translation,
press / blog coverage, academic discussion, screenshots, or derivative
works — please open a GitHub issue or contact zikedece@proton.me. We
respond to good-faith requests quickly.

Fair-use commentary, journalism, and accessibility-related reuse never
require permission.

----------------------------------------------------------------

The third-party software linked from the website (Apple system voices,
AVFoundation, PDFKit, StoreKit, SwiftData, SwiftUI) belongs to its
respective owners. Sample books bundled with the iOS app are
public-domain works — see the in-app About panel and the README for
provenance.
